sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant API as Astro API
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2

    A->>API: POST /api/presign
    API->>R2: Génère URL signée S3 (TTL 3600s)
    R2-->>API: URL signée
    API-->>A: URL signée
    Note over A,R2: Upload direct — ne transite pas par le serveur
    A->>R2: PUT photo (JPEG original)
    Note over R2: Cache-Control: immutable, max-age=31536000
    A->>API: PUT /api/albums/{slug}
    API->>R2: Màj albums/{slug}.json + index.json
    API-->>A: 200 OK
